sentences: Dannell Stevens (born December 12, 1969), better known as D-Shot, is an American rapper from Vallejo, California.
D-Shot's debut album, The Shot Calla, was released in 1993 through Sick Wid It Records.
In 1995, D-Shot formed his own label, Shot Records, where he released his second album, Six Figures, in 1997.
